Miss real food! Don't like bland human and elfy food, though do like spiced humans and elves!

Really crave some orcan jerky. Took some when I left, but ran out. Sooo goooood!

Maybe you bring me more?

Oh, yes! At last! Thank you!

Yum. Soooo good. You want? Promise, no elf or human in there.
I just want orcan jerky. Know there's some where my people gather. Orcans have great taste.
